# ───────────────────────────────────────────────
# Planet-Play .gitignore
# Keeps compiled output, logs, and OS junk out of the repo.
# Only source code, the README, and game assets should be tracked.
# ───────────────────────────────────────────────

# Compiled executable (SplashKit build output — no file extension).
# The leading slash anchors this to the repo root, so it only ignores
# the binary and never a folder that happens to share the name.
/planet-play

# Debug symbol bundles (created on macOS builds)
*.dSYM/

# Runtime / SplashKit logs
*.log
logs/
myeasylog.log

# macOS / editor / OS junk
.DS_Store
._*
__MACOSX/
.vscode/